---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Hingamiskeskuse liikmelisus | Hingamiskeskus">

<header class="header">
  <a href="/" class="header__logo">
    <img src="/images/logo.svg" alt="Hingamiskeskus" height="30" />
  </a>
  <nav class="header__nav">
    <a href="/">Avaleht</a>
    <a href="/teenused">Teenused</a>
    <a href="/broneeri-aeg">Broneeri aeg</a>
    <a href="/e-pood">E-pood</a>
    <a href="/hakka-liikmeks" class="active">Hakka liikmeks</a>
    <a href="/paketid">Paketid</a>
    <a href="/blogi">Blogi</a>
    <a href="/kkk">KKK</a>
  </nav>
  <div class="header__right">
    <a href="/e-pood" class="header__cart" aria-label="Ostukorv">
      <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <path d="M6 2L3 6v14a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2V6l-3-4z"/><line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/><path d="M16 10a4 4 0 01-8 0"/>
      </svg>
    </a>
    <button class="header__burger" aria-label="Menüü">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </button>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="membership">
  <div class="membership__layout">
    <div class="membership__content">
      <h1>Hingamiskeskuse liikmelisus</h1>

      <h2>Mida liikmelisus sisaldab?</h2>
      <p>Liikmelisuse kuutasu on <strong>59 €</strong>, mis sisaldab <strong>kahte seanssi kuus</strong>. Üks floatingu seanss ja üks grupihingamisseanss <strong>(tavahind kokku 80 €)</strong>.</p>

      <p>Lisaks:</p>
      <div class="membership__benefits">
        <p>Piiramatu arv floatingu seansse 30€ kord</p>
        <p>Piiramatu arv grupihingamisseansse 30€ kord</p>
        <p>Kinkekaardid liikmetele 15% soodustus</p>
        <p>Kasutamata floatingud kehtivad 1 aasta</p>
        <p>Sõbra kaasavõtmine 30€</p>
        <p>3-kuuline siduvus, 1-kuuline ülesütlemise aeg</p>
        <p>Võimalus liikmelisus ajutiselt peatada (kuni 3 kuud aastas)</p>
      </div>

      <a href="#" class="membership__btn" id="hakka-btn">HAKKA LIIKMEKS</a>
    </div>

    <div class="membership__side">
      <img src="/images/dscf6099.jpg" alt="Hingamiskeskus floating" class="membership__image" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="membership__terms">
    <h2>Tingimused</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Liikmelisus on <strong>isiklik</strong> ega ole edasiantav ilma Hingamiskeskuse loata.</li>
      <li>Kasutamata floatingud kehtivad 1 <strong>aastat</strong>, kuid neid ei kompenseerita rahaliselt.</li>
      <li>Hingamiskeskusel on õigus hindu muuta, teavitades sellest aegsasti.</li>
      <li>Kui keskus peab remondi tõttu olema suletud kuni <strong>7 päeva</strong>, ei mõjuta see liikmemaksu. Pikema sulgemise korral pakutakse liikmetele võimalust kohene liikmelisuse tühistamine.</li>
      <li>Liikmelisust saab peatada kuni <strong>3 kuuks aastas</strong>, teavitades sellest kirjalikult (<a href="mailto:info@hingamiskeskus.ee">info@hingamiskeskus.ee</a>).</li>
      <li>Kehtib tähtajatult, ülesütlemise tähtaeg <strong>1 kalendrikuu</strong>.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="footer">
  <div class="location">
    <h3 class="location__title">Aadress</h3>
    <p class="location__address">Söle 14c, Tallinn</p>
    <img src="/images/hoone.jpg" alt="Hingamiskeskus Söle 14c" class="location__photo" loading="lazy" />
  </div>
  <div class="footer__main">
    <img src="/images/logo-valge.png" alt="Hingamiskeskus" class="footer__logo" />
    <div class="footer__contact">
      <h3>Kontakt</h3>
      <p>E-post: Info@hingamiskeskus.ee</p>
      <p>Telefoninumber:</p>
      <p>+372 56695898</p>
      <p>+372 56497689</p>
      <p>(klienditugi 10.00-17.00)</p>
      <p>Hingamises OÜ</p>
      <p>EE147700771009732310</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer__hours">
      <h3>Lahtiolekuajad</h3>
      <p>E-R 8.30 - 20.00</p>
      <p>L-P 11.00 - 18.00</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer__social">
      <a href="https://www.facebook.com/Hingamiskeskus" aria-label="Facebook" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"/></svg>
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/hingamiskeskus/" aria-label="Instagram" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"/><circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="1.5" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer__legal">
      <a href="/privaatsuspoliitika">Privaatsuspoliitika</a> | <a href="/muugitingimused">Müügitingimused</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

</Layout>

<style>
  .header {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 10px 16px; background: #fff; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }
  .header__logo img { height: 28px; width: auto; }
  .header__nav {
    display: none;
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .header__nav a {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #1d1e20;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .header__nav a.active {
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 4px;
  }
  .header__right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
  .header__cart { color: #1d1e20; }
  .header__burger { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; padding: 4px; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; }
  .header__burger span { display: block; width: 22px; height: 2px; background: #1d1e20; }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .header__nav { display: flex; }
    .header__burger { display: none; }
  }

  .membership {
    padding: 40px 24px;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .membership__layout {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .membership__layout {
      flex-direction: row;
      gap: 60px;
    }
    .membership__content { flex: 3; }
    .membership__side { flex: 2; }
  }

  .membership h1 {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    color: #1d1e20;
  }

  .membership h2 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: #1d1e20;
  }

  .membership p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .membership ul {
    padding-left: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .membership li {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .membership a {
    color: #1f6d85;
  }

  .membership__btn {
    color: #fff !important;
  }

  .membership__benefits p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .membership__terms {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px 40px;
  }

  .membership__terms h2 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: #1d1e20;
  }

  .membership__terms ul {
    padding-left: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .membership__terms li {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .membership__terms a {
    color: #1f6d85;
  }

  .membership__image {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 10px;
    object-fit: cover;
    max-height: 500px;
  }

  .membership__btn {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    background: #1d1e20;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    padding: 16px 32px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-top: 28px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .location {
    background: #1f6d85;
    padding: 20px 24px 24px;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .location__title {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .location__address {
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  .location__photo {
    width: 80%;
    max-width: 320px;
    margin: 12px auto 0;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 10px;
  }
  .footer__main {
    background: #1f6d85;
    padding: 24px;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .footer__logo {
    height: 30px;
    width: auto;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
    display: block;
  }
  .footer__contact h3,
  .footer__hours h3 {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .footer__contact p,
  .footer__hours p {
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .footer__hours {
    margin-top: 16px;
  }
  .footer__social {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 16px;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .footer__legal {
    font-size: 11px;
    margin-top: 16px;
    opacity: 0.7;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    padding-top: 12px;
  }
  .footer__legal a { color: #fff; text-decoration: none; }
  .footer__legal a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
</style>
